data.description: Welcome to 501 Barhams Ridge Drive, a stunning 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home located in the desirable community of Barhams Ridge in McDonough, Georgia. This immaculate property offers both curb appeal and luxury finishes, making it the perfect place to call home. As you step through the front door, you'll be greeted by a grand foyer that leads into the spacious and light-filled living room. The living room features soaring ceilings, a cozy fireplace, and large windows that provide an abundance of natural light. The living room flows seamlessly into the rest of the home, making it perfect for entertaining guests. The gourmet kitchen is a chef's dream, with a large center island, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and plenty of storage space. The kitchen also features a breakfast bar and an undercounted area for 2 wine fridges. The primary bedroom of the 4 total, features large tray ceilings and a spa-like en suite bathroom with dual vanities, a garden tub, separate shower, and his and hers walk in closets! There's also a bonus room that's perfect for a home office, sun room, or den. Outside, the property truly shines with a large, level backyard that's perfect for gardening, playing, or hosting barbecues. The home also includes a two-car garage, ensuring that you'll have plenty of space for storage and parking. Located just minutes from the charming downtown McDonough, this property is ideally situated for those who value both privacy and convenience. You'll be just a short drive from shops, restaurants, and entertainment, as well as major highways that can take you to Atlanta and beyond. Don't miss your chance to make this stunning property your own - schedule a showing today!
